author: chsigg
message:
Add new dependencies to `workspace2.bzl`.

This change adds `fmt`, `kokkos`, `raft`, `rapids_logger`, `rmm`, and `spdlog` to the TensorFlow workspace dependencies.

PiperOrigin-RevId: 805700543
